## Step 1 — `tenant_organization` (create first)

**UI:** Primary `www.event-site-manager.com` → **Admin → Tenant Management → Organizations**

**API (prod or local JWT):**

```http
POST /api/tenant-organizations
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <service_jwt>

{
  "tenantId": "<TENANT_ID>",
  "organizationName": "<ORG_NAME>",
  "domain": "www.<apex>.com",
  "contactEmail": "<contact@example.com>",
  "contactPhone": "+1-555-0100",
  "websiteUrl": "https://www.<apex>.com",
  "logoUrl": "https://<bucket-or-cdn>/logo.png",
  "primaryColor": "#2563eb",
  "secondaryColor": "#111827",
  "siteType": "EVENT_ORG",
  "isActive": true
}
```

**Verify:**

```http
GET /api/tenant-organizations?tenantId.equals=<TENANT_ID>&size=1
```

**Local SQL verify:**

```powershell
docker exec event_site_manager_db-postgresql-1 psql -U postgres -d event_site_manager_db -c "
SELECT id, tenant_id, organization_name, domain, contact_email, logo_url
FROM tenant_organization WHERE tenant_id = '<TENANT_ID>';
"
```

---

## Step 2 — `tenant_settings` (link to org)

**UI:** Admin → Tenant Management → **Settings** (same `tenantId`, link `tenantOrganization: { id: <org_id> }`)

**Minimum fields:**

| Field | Suggested dev value |
|-------|---------------------|
| `tenantId` | `<TENANT_ID>` |
| `tenantOrganizationId` | org `id` from step 1 |
| `email` | contact email |
| `phoneNumber` | contact phone |
| `allowUserRegistration` | `true` |
| `requireAdminApproval` | `false` (dev) / `true` (prod policy) |
| `showEventsSectionInHomePage` | per product (Globex marketing sites may ignore) |
| `logoImageUrl` | same as org logo |
| `enableGuestRegistration` | `true` |

**Verify:**

```http
GET /api/tenant-settings?tenantId.equals=<TENANT_ID>&size=1
```

---

## Step 3 — `tenant_email_addresses` (contact forms + outbound email)

Required for contact-form batch jobs (`emailType` = `CONTACT`). Add at least:

| `email_type` | `email_address` | `is_default` | `is_active` |
|--------------|-----------------|--------------|-------------|
| `CONTACT` | contact email | `true` | `true` |
| `INFO` | contact email | `true` | `true` |
| `NOREPLY` | `noreply@<domain>` or contact | `true` | `true` |

**API:**

```http
POST /api/tenant-email-addresses
```

**Local SQL example (after org exists):**

```sql
INSERT INTO tenant_email_addresses (tenant_id, email_type, email_address, is_default, is_active, created_at, updated_at)
VALUES
  ('<TENANT_ID>', 'CONTACT', '<contact@example.com>', true, true, NOW(), NOW()),
  ('<TENANT_ID>', 'INFO',    '<contact@example.com>', true, true, NOW(), NOW())
ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING;
```

