## Step 7 — Smoke verification

| Check | Pass criteria |
|-------|----------------|
| Tenant org | GET `tenant-organizations?tenantId.equals=...` ≥ 1 row |
| Tenant settings | GET `tenant-settings?tenantId.equals=...` ≥ 1 row |
| Admin status | Signed in → `GET /api/auth/admin-status` → `{ "isAdmin": true }` |
| Admin menu | Header shows **Admin** dropdown (not only profile avatar) |
| Admin panel | `GET /admin` → 200 (not Access Denied) |
| Proxy | `GET /api/proxy/tenant-settings` → 200 |
| Contact email | `tenant_email_addresses` has `CONTACT` default for tenant |
| Logo | Org/settings `logo_url` / `logo_image_url` set; site header shows logo |
| Calendar link | Optional: one test event → “Add to calendar” opens Google Calendar URL |

**After DB role change:** hard refresh or sign out/in so `isTenantAdmin` / `useHeaderAuth` picks up ADMIN.

