## Frontend env alignment

Satellite / marketing site `.env.local` minimum:

```bash
NEXT_PUBLIC_TENANT_ID=<TENANT_ID>
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080   # local
API_JWT_USER=jwtadmin
API_JWT_PASS=<dev_secret>
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_PUBLISHABLE_KEY=pk_test_...
CLERK_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
# Satellite only:
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_IS_SATELLITE=true
NEXT_PUBLIC_PRIMARY_DOMAIN=www.event-site-manager.com
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_IN_URL=https://www.event-site-manager.com/sign-in
NEXT_PUBLIC_CLERK_SIGN_UP_URL=https://www.event-site-manager.com/sign-up
```

`NEXT_PUBLIC_TENANT_ID` must match every DB row and Admin → Satellite Domains record.

